<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_05_SU_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema614_05_0005.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema614_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema614_05_su_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3">
            <div>
                <span lang="y">하늘시와 바다시의 인구와 넓이를 나타낸 표입니다. 두 도시의 넓이에 대한 인구의 비율을 비교해 봅시다.</span>
                <button type="button" class="btn calculator">계산기</button>
            </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <h3 lang="y">
                기준량과 비교하는 양은 각각 무엇인지 이야기해 보세요.
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="table_box">
                  <table>
                    <colgroup>
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                    </colgroup>
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">도시</th>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">하늘시</th>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">바다시</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="row">인구 (명)</th>
                        <td>2500000​</td>
                        <td>1740000​</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="row">넓이 (㎢)</th>
                        <td>1600</td>
                        <td>1200</td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col">
                    <span class="f32b">기준량: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="넓이"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col">
                    <span class="f32b">비교하는 양: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="인구"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="page page_2">
              <h3 lang="y">
                두 도시의 넓이에 대한 인구의 비율을 각각 구해 보세요.
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="table_box">
                  <table>
                    <colgroup>
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                    </colgroup>
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">도시</th>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">하늘시</th>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">바다시</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="row">인구 (명)</th>
                        <td>2500000​</td>
                        <td>1740000​</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="row">넓이 (㎢)</th>
                        <td>1600</td>
                        <td>1200</td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col">
                    <span class="f32b">하늘시: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="(2500000)/(1600)" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["(2500000)/(1600)", "(3125)/(2)", "1562.5"]}' data-multi-hint="y" ></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col">
                    <span class="f32b">바다시: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="(1740000)/(1200)" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["(1740000)/(1200)", "1450"]}' data-multi-hint="y" ></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
              <h3 lang="y">
                도시의 넓이에 대한 인구의 비율이 낮아질수록 같은 넓이에 대한 인구는 어떻게 달라질지 이야기해 보세요.​
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="table_box">
                  <table>
                    <colgroup>
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                      <col style="width: 276px;">
                    </colgroup>
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">도시</th>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">하늘시</th>
                        <th lang="y" scope="col">바다시</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="row">인구 (명)</th>
                        <td>2500000​</td>
                        <td>1740000​</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <th lang="y" scope="row">넓이 (㎢)</th>
                        <td>1600</td>
                        <td>1200</td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                  <div class="example_box">
                      <p>도시의 넓이에 대한 인구의 비율이 낮아질수록 같은 넓이에 대한 인구는 더 적어집니다.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              </div>
            </article>

        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
